{"tid":1310981,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"明明武力就係解決問題嘅最佳方法！所以政府先會宣傳反對暴力。","createTime":"2019-07-13T03:06:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-18T15:18:10.000Z","uid":43785,"like":299,"dislike":26,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"cfcaf139e7be919f0b5e94172bfa290562c1d091","tid":1310981,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:06:30.000Z","msg":"明明武力就係解決問題嘅最佳方法！<br />\n所以政府先會宣傳反對暴力。<br />\n<br />\n明明惡法係因為武力令佢撤回。偏偏和理非不去相信事實。<br />\n市民多少自殺是不管的，根本林鄭只驚有警察受傷。<br />\n<br />\n政府不懼怕擺工擺市，也不懼怕一百萬人，更不懼怕二百萬人<br />\n只懼怕612，5萬人，當中就算是只有一小部份人衝擊警察，令警察受傷。他就立即暫緩了惡法。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自古以來，對抗獨裁都係打番來的。<br />\n<br />\n革命不是請客吃飯，<br />\n當年你踢水貨客驅趕大陸人，梁震英推限奶令。<br />\n你郁手驅趕大媽，政府廢自娛區。<br />\n你打警察，林鄭暫緩送中。<br />\n<br />\n在獨裁國家，沒有不動手就能取勝的革命。<br />\n搞獨立也好，搞革命也好，沒有流血，沒有成果。<br />\n二百萬人上街，政府沒有回應訴求，沒有達到目的，也沒有警察喪生，在外國看來是笑話。<br />\n<br />\n香港需要的是大規模的不合作對抗運動。<br />\n我不批評連儂牆，但我們發現建連儂牆多日，政府沒有回應五大訴求，就要再想想新方法。<br />\n<br />\n記住，守的不是我們，守的是政府，我們的做法是要令政府頭痛，逐步升級，迫他出來解決問題。<br />\n<br />\n我們每出黎亂一次，建制就分化一次，每流一滴血也是有價值的。<br />\n<br />\n有人說我們失敗了，乜我們成功過嗎？<br />\n警察濫權殺人，槍槍爆頭誰去查？<br />\n記住我們呢二百萬人就是為了成功才走出來。<br />\n有五條人命先後離開，都是為了我們有成功既一日。<br />\n六十七個被捕義士（或更多人）仍然有可能會因為林鄭施政失敗，而代林鄭坐十年暴動監。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n未死既你，別讓義士冤枉犧牲，請行出來積極參與民間運動，迫林鄭答應市民五大訴求。"},{"pid":"6cc02f3fb1afd826ee2211d9e1f8fa264ad46ef8","tid":1310981,"uid":17732,"like":84,"dislike":2,"score":82,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:08:26.000Z","msg":"比d時間香港人<br />\n始終大家都係溫室大<br />\n當大家都唔驚死，上前線抗爭<br />\n咩政府都要收皮"},{"pid":"5b3855c04e0af5c51dd70825b34787a849e996f4","tid":1310981,"uid":43785,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:08:55.000Z","msg":"今日，出上水，光復上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e28463b9a2b559dba62800061bf9a9fe4ab0d1f","tid":1310981,"uid":196578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:10:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0cb5d16e46317c9dc656522f88297e2a595187ae","tid":1310981,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5b3855c04e0af5c51dd70825b34787a849e996f4","tid":1310981,"uid":43785,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:08:55.000Z","msg":"今日，出上水，光復上水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:10:23.000Z","msg":"如果柴灣出發係咪去到九龍塘轉車最快？"},{"pid":"33d7d8c398007700ff6a20f224fd39ad247370f1","tid":1310981,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:10:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2573ce8c2cf0ecf6767f0780fac31fee7fe0ee1b","tid":1310981,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:11:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0444394e3b3958952f6581ee3f534e22a02ee851","tid":1310981,"uid":262557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc13fe9076e314cb0f91abc3ce962cf888fec464","tid":1310981,"uid":43785,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"6cc02f3fb1afd826ee2211d9e1f8fa264ad46ef8","tid":1310981,"uid":17732,"like":84,"dislike":2,"score":82,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:08:26.000Z","msg":"比d時間香港人<br />\n始終大家都係溫室大<br />\n當大家都唔驚死，上前線抗爭<br />\n咩政府都要收皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:15:38.000Z","msg":"都係果句，你唔亂，政府就當睇唔到。<br />\n你愈亂，政府先會回應。<br />\n<br />\n講到尾到你用槍指住習近平金正恩，佢點都要聽你講。<br />\n問題就係香港人如何成為一支可以指住林鄭，指住盧偉聰既槍。<br />\n<br />\n我知道要時間，但希望香港人真係要識醒。<br />\n唔好守一D無謂既野。令成個抗爭由攻轉守。<br />\n<br />\n你擺個盾牌喺林鄭月娥面前，人哋唔會驚你。"},{"pid":"5e96ef372c7ef9799211d299c4e6874d27faf215","tid":1310981,"uid":40902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:16:33.000Z","msg":"不再善忘呀香港人"},{"pid":"bc1c71ac2a99e2611ab3a880952e157fffb6ed8c","tid":1310981,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e96ef372c7ef9799211d299c4e6874d27faf215","tid":1310981,"uid":40902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:16:33.000Z","msg":"不再善忘呀香港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:20:40.000Z","msg":"係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a81002af2532fa23ba0425fc33430c0ce921f0fc","tid":1310981,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:27:33.000Z","msg":"我冇野講"},{"pid":"d2484845604d8b7c5f9234b20d93d1c300d1a596","tid":1310981,"uid":12149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f9b3d7da0d4c5f99c8ea820d65b26218396d79","tid":1310981,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:30:30.000Z","msg":"鳩sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地一齊贏<br />\n然後你繼續除暴安良好冇"},{"pid":"a43fe342c83fb84a0c3f0510fb83b99497379e68","tid":1310981,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"29f9b3d7da0d4c5f99c8ea820d65b26218396d79","tid":1310981,"uid":183576,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:30:30.000Z","msg":"鳩sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />我地一齊贏<br />\n然後你繼續除暴安良好冇"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:41:54.000Z","msg":"一齊贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cd65b309f387e5c2c5b106fdb2a82ca5004a82f","tid":1310981,"uid":43785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T03:58:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c57bb8f991bd8c5353e934f5bfd213726ed16869","tid":1310981,"uid":70403,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-13T04: